<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٣٢٣ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{جَعَلَ السِّقَايَةَ}</span> <span class="c4">[يوسف: ٧٠]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مِشْرَبَةُ الْمَلِكِ إِنَاءٌ»</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَصُوَاعُ الْمَلِكِ إِنَاءُ الْمَلِكِ الَّذِي يَشْرَبُ فِيهِ "<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>